<br>
I was not trying to *fix* anything.  In fact, I never once flamed, accused or approached the Vets to change their hate raid.  I'm sorry if you took it that I was challenging anyone.  As I said in my original post I was willing to reschedule our raid because we had in fact double booked a plane...no biggie.<br>
<br>
It was an honest mistake that the raid was booked for the same day.  Stony booked the raid and obviously didn't notice that hate was already booked.  I personally wasn't aware that there was a problem until someone emailed regarding it.  I only came here looking for the post that listed the raid calendar guidelines so I could be more aware of the restrictions.  I was not a guild leader when the guidelines were created and wasn't fully aware of all the ins and outs.  I fully support the calendar, hence the reason I was looking for the guidelines.  Thank you for the link.<br>
<br>
I was not trying to point fingers, or accusing any guild of abusing the calendar.  Mistakes happen, plain and simple.  If the Vets would like to raid hate on Jan 6th, feel free.  We have made alternate plans for that day on the assumption that we were in the wrong for double booking a plane.  Stony's reservation came second, I was more than happy to bow out.  <br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
I am a very reasonable person and I would hope that if anyone has a problem with myself, my posts, my booking raids, my guild, whatever, that they would approach me to discuss it.    <p><center><img src="http://phrogie.20m.com/nemesys/pics/KeleAni.gif"></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ukelestra.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kelestra</A> at: 1/3/02 1:09:20 pm<br></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335dragonsandtheplanes.showMessage?topicID=791.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335dragonsandtheplanes.showMessage?topicID=1049.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335dragonsandtheplanes.emailToFriend?topicID=1039.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335dragonsandtheplanes.threadControl?topicID=1039.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/deleteThreadFire.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335dragonsandtheplanes.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1039.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335dragonsandtheplanes.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1039.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub6.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="luclin71335general">General<option value="l